{"tid":2412410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登口誤？美國官媒澄清他確實向習近平談及台港新疆問題","createTime":"2021-02-18T04:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T13:42:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"d383481c7c4c050e1f5446de3915932bb820a5db","tid":2412410,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"美國總統拜登周二（2/16）在CNN節目上一番談及中國人權和台港問題的言論引發熱烈討論。由於拜登未清楚說明完整句子，一度讓外界以為他不會為台港發聲，但美國官方媒體美國之音和自由亞洲電台中文版均在隨後的報導指出，拜登確實在與中國國家主席習近平的通話中，關切中國在香港、新疆及武力威脅台灣行徑。<br />\n<br />\n根據CNN影片及白宮的逐字文稿，拜登在被主持人問及是否和習近平討論人權問題時表示：「我向他（習近平）表明：沒有一個美國總統，能在不反映美國價值下繼續當總統。所以這種想法，我不會發言反對他在香港、在中國西部維吾爾族，以及企圖武力解決台灣問題、藉此終結（美國）一中政策的種種行為&hellip;我說&hellip;他說他了解。從文化上來看，每一個國家的領導人都有不同的遵循模式。」（I point out to him: No American President can be sustained as a President if he doesn&rsquo;t reflect the values of the United States. And so the idea I&rsquo;m not going to speak out against what he&rsquo;s doing in Hong Kong, what he&rsquo;s doing with the Uyghurs in western mountains of China and Taiwan, trying to end the One China policy by making it forceful &mdash; I said &mdash; and by the &mdash; he said he &mdash; he gets it. Culturally, there are different norms that each country and they &mdash; their leaders &mdash; are expected to follow. ）<br />\n<br />\n由於拜登在這段發言中，並未完整說明究竟是否向習近平提及香港、新疆和台灣問題，使得外界一度以為他向北京屈服。<br />\n<br />\n不過美國之音和自由亞洲電台的中文報導則是清楚指出，拜登「向習近平表達了對中國打壓新疆、香港和台灣的關注」。報導同時強調，拜登向習近平表明，中國對人權的打壓將會面臨後果，而他（習近平）知道這一點。<br />\n<br />\n不過報導也提及，拜登這段提及「每個國家領導人遵循不同的文化差異」內容，受到美國部分保守派人士批評。他們將這番話解讀成拜登為習近平箝制自由、踐踏人權的行為辯解。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210218/L2YFKARYBNCKNMA6V66BLZNMC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210218%2FL2YFKARYBNCKNMA6V66BLZNMC4%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=e2782a8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210218%2FL2YFKARYBNCKNMA6V66BLZNMC4%2F&h=0b5a75ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210218/L2YFKARYBNCKNMA6V66BLZNMC4/</a>"},{"pid":"c155cc5fd3b050ecf8ad2424433bddf46dd44959","tid":2412410,"uid":77196,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"痴呆發作"},{"pid":"f974b803c76e5f18418e16201bf14c7f4c8a9017","tid":2412410,"uid":38982,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"第二鑊啦, 總統講錯野要人補鑊, 拜登死左佢啦"},{"pid":"4020af440eb4fb66e5ea2fa0fab103313187de38","tid":2412410,"uid":114275,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"已經好樣衰 咪兜啦好心"},{"pid":"e63d9f27da7ee6df64527704b4a0563d1b7118b4","tid":2412410,"uid":248540,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:47:57.000Z","msg":"美國之音=奶共"},{"pid":"10ab80174cac79f1a7ed6d2d5ab62fe0133dfb23","tid":2412410,"uid":8014,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"見肥佬黎又被捕 又高調用国安法拉人就知佢地已經傾掂數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家直程連出Twitter 都廢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d63004b14b4fd2c0847b368dce31d32f65355e","tid":2412410,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"佢係講到1999<br />\n但個意思唔係連登仔所理解咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ccc64c0da69243531d2ccbf2053dbc62027cf8","tid":2412410,"uid":7369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"屌你, 次次做訪問都口誤學乜人選總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b050615226e9d4cfaba5d23a69cda4d43d4bd3","tid":2412410,"uid":186882,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e63d9f27da7ee6df64527704b4a056